properties.name: Old Monastery
properties.description: The primitive Desert Monastery built between 1697 and 1733. The complex had capacity for some twenty-four monks. In 1783 a series of torrential rains and earthquakes caused serious damage to the structure of the building, and the Barefoot Carmelites were obliged to leave.
